{"tid":1801347,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"理大報告已出！！","createTime":"2019-12-28T14:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T15:40:01.000Z","uid":65204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e55c5c0aa22beb9097278bb23edcf4e655bed9","tid":1801347,"uid":65204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"各位同學、各位同事 :<br />\n<br />\n<strong>首批校園環境評估檢試結果</strong><br />\n<br />\n為確保學生和教職員享有健康安全的校園環境，並釋除對校園內殘留催淚氣體有害物質的疑慮，香港理工大學（理大）在 11 月 29 日 收回 校園後，於 12 月初委託獨立認可實驗室 在 校園內進行了一系列的環境檢測，其中包括在校園不同地點採集了空氣、水、土壤和擦拭 測試的樣本作檢測 。 測試包括以下污染物：<br />\n<br />\na. 二噁英<br />\nb. 總多氯聯苯<br />\nc. 多環芳香烴<br />\nd. 總氰化物<br />\ne. 鄰-氯代苯亞甲基丙二腈（CS）<br />\n<br />\n以下總結了土壤（ S1-S8）、自來水（WA1-WA4）和表面擦拭（W1-W22）樣本的測試結果。尚未收到的結果在下列中顯示為「檢測中」， 我們預計將於明年 1 月收到有 關 結果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjwDz4Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhjwDz4Q.png&h=9e72e460&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/28/222540_51e17e966fa64d25781278c9347b22d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F28%2F222540_51e17e966fa64d25781278c9347b22d5.png&h=84231b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n註一 : 日本二噁英環境標準規定的參考水平（年度）為 0.6 皮克 TEQ/ 立方米 <br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>結論</strong></span> <br />\n根據測試結果，並參照本地或國際相關政府部門或機構所訂定的認可標準，有關土壤（ S1-S8 ）、自來水（ WA1-WA4 ），和擦拭（ W1-W22 ）樣本內含有以上提及的污染物，以及在空氣樣本中所含的 CS 粉末 ，均遠低於相關的安全標準限值 。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww1j3YM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww1j3YM.png&h=b25c7262&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"808eabe0ad5fe7694c2111a633e86fadabec2adf","tid":1801347,"uid":65204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"第二張手殘cut柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cdFOqS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cdFOqS.png&h=0ac4907c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9e1764f58c7e53f720ecc2e87149d2c857b4457","tid":1801347,"uid":289021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"起碼唔洗番學都要生cancer先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058568f48d8cecb400072f4a508df117c969c178","tid":1801347,"uid":65204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"有無化學JJ解讀下係咪真係無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6386011f01eae9607d4f1399780303e2ad8c47e0","tid":1801347,"uid":65204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddfecdb8c8857c2952bba57980b1f9cf0cab5e6","tid":1801347,"uid":65204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"正經post無人推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5466cd9634bc6be70554da72de9b94bc3c3d1b2d","tid":1801347,"uid":89131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"旺角一樣多殘留tg 咪一樣照出"},{"pid":"f68021c0b5be04d97344700276b8dbe798d6e5d6","tid":1801347,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5466cd9634bc6be70554da72de9b94bc3c3d1b2d","tid":1801347,"uid":89131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"旺角一樣多殘留tg 咪一樣照出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:10:36.000Z","msg":"越多人幫手吸收越快無"},{"pid":"0345281ab93d00e3f837eb12d33333bba6d28fd2","tid":1801347,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"推"}